WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
My name is Fulton Skikos. I was an RA last year at the Yak Community Building 172d, or Chikukunitch.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
If I'm being honest, I didn't really enjoy being an RA at all. It was very difficult.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Each day came with various challenges that I just really wasn't up for.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:22.000
I had to help this one freshman who got back from a party, and she was throwing up for hours and hours.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:29.000
It ended up in the sink, which is pretty nasty. I had to personally clean it up.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:34.000
I didn't want the housekeeper to come in and be like, "What the hell is this?"

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:42.000
I really think that Cal Poly should do a better job of fixing this program and making it more rewarding.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:49.000
People dedicate their year to looking out for the freshmen, and in return I don't get crap.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:54.000
Except for free housing and a free meal plan. Even that was, I mean, the food here sucks.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:58.000
The biggest highlight was handing out scented pencils at the end of each quarter for the check-ins.
